+/*
+ * SOO hypercall
+ *
+ * Mandatory arguments:
+ * - cmd: hypercall
+ * - addr: a virtual address used within the hypervisor
+ * - p_val1: a (virtual) address to a first value
+ * - p_val2: a (virtual) address to a second value
+ */
+
